MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Update uniswap intent guidance to explicitly prioritize crypto-lp.fetch_positions
  tick data (P25–P75 liquidity-weighted distribution) as primary range source
- Only fall back to OHLCV-based volatility analysis when position data is missing
- Update crypto-lp.fetch_positions tool description to reinforce the priority order
- Update test assertions to match new description text

